    <h2>1. Services</h2>
    <p>
        FlowSync Consulting provides custom NetSuite development services including, but not limited to, custom Suitelets, workflow automation, system integration, document generation, and performance optimization consulting.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Engagement Types</h2>
    <p>Services are provided through one of the following engagement models:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Project-Based:</strong> Fixed scope, timeline, and budget as defined in the project proposal.</li>
        <li><strong>Retainer:</strong> Ongoing monthly capacity for development, support, and optimization work.</li>
        <li><strong>Hourly Consulting:</strong> Services billed at agreed hourly rates for ad-hoc needs.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        All engagements begin with a signed proposal or statement of work (SOW) that outlines deliverables, timeline, and compensation.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Payment Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Project-Based:</strong> 50% deposit required before work begins. Remaining 50% due upon project completion and client acceptance.</li>
        <li><strong>Retainer:</strong> Monthly retainer invoiced at the beginning of each billing period. Payment due within 15 days of invoice date.</li>
        <li><strong>Hourly Consulting:</strong> Invoiced monthly. Payment due within 15 days of invoice date.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        Accepted payment methods: ACH transfer, credit card (via Stripe), check. Late payments may incur a 1.5% monthly interest charge.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Refund and Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Project-Based:</strong> Initial deposit is non-refundable once work has begun. If the project is cancelled mid-stream, client is responsible for payment of work completed to date at the agreed hourly equivalent rate.</li>
        <li><strong>Retainer:</strong> Either party may cancel with 30 days written notice. Unused retainer hours do not roll over to subsequent months unless otherwise specified in the SOW.</li>
        <li><strong>Hourly Consulting:</strong> No refunds for completed work. Client may terminate the engagement at any time and will be invoiced for hours worked to date.</li>
    </ul>

